    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十一月二十二日　昼",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1600.0000556,
          "startTime": 2.4000000556
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4400,
          "startTime": 5.2
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6400,
          "startTime": 7.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん、この辺にしよっか。んしょ……\nじゃーん、みんなで作ったお弁当～",
      "startTime": 7.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……！　ありがとう！\nいつの間に作ったの？　全然気が付かなかったよ～",
      "startTime": 13.8666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんが、出掛けた後に作った\nリハがあるって知ってたから、その時間を狙って",
      "startTime": 21.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだぁ。あ、怜ちゃんも作ってくれてる\nつい微笑ましくて、10カワって言っちゃったのに",
      "startTime": 29.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "ぷりぷりしてたけど、怒ってなかったよ。というか\n焼き魚を見ただけで怜ちゃんのだと見抜くなんてさすが",
      "startTime": 39.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、表面が焦げ……よ、よく焼けてたから\nでも、なんだか雫ちゃんのお誕生日を思い出すね",
      "startTime": 50.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "うん。あの時は千紗ちゃんが、みんなとお弁当を\n作ってくれたよね。だから、そのお返しも兼ねてる",
      "startTime": 58.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "それと、渚ちゃんが言ってたんだけど……\n……っ……や、やっぱり、なんでもない……",
      "startTime": 69.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "……？　渚ちゃんが何か言ってたの？\n今日のソロライブのこと？",
      "startTime": 77.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうじゃなくて……その……\nじゃあ……笑わない……？　へ、変に思わない？",
      "startTime": 84.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "うん、笑わないし、変にも思わないよ？",
      "startTime": 90.0666596652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、えっと……っ……\n千紗ちゃん、あーん……して。た、食べさせてあげる",
      "startTime": 97.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "え……えぇぇ！？\nなっ、え、あの、え、雫ちゃん！？",
      "startTime": 107.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり忘れて！",
      "startTime": 111.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違うの雫ちゃん！　変に思ったとかじゃなくて\n単純にびっくりしちゃって。えっと、食べればいいの？",
      "startTime": 117.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん、渚ちゃんが、こういうことしたら\n千紗ちゃんが喜んでくれるかもって言うから……",
      "startTime": 127.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9133.333333300001,
          "startTime": 136.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "で、で、でも、急に変だし、無理しなくて大丈夫\nライブ前に何やってるのって話だし……って、わぁ！？",
      "startTime": 134.6952088203,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4471.450844900005,
          "startTime": 139.1666596652
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "あーん……ん～、美味しい……！　えへへ、ちょっと\n照れちゃうけど、雫ちゃんとはこういうこと初めてだね",
      "startTime": 146.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "っ……そ、そう、だね。琴乃ちゃんと渚ちゃんとか\n瑠依さんと優ちゃんが、たまにしてるの見るけど",
      "startTime": 157.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、仲良しって感じがするし\n私達も、たまにはいいのかもね。はい雫ちゃん、あ～ん",
      "startTime": 165.1379763207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　わ、私もするの……！？\n待って、恥ずかし過ぎるから、ちょっとだけ待って",
      "startTime": 175,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}